{"tid":1563180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實人鏈洗唔洗日日搞呀","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:43:27.000Z","uid":146917,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c068bc72a8b1e88fd4756f06f1bb36b7ac7fd0","tid":1563180,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"本身唔係只想迎合果一個外國活動炸咩？<br />\n搞完一次變左日常化咁<br />\n有一種唔應該變成咁嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n其他活動冇咩意見"},{"pid":"9da306642eda0097d45c4b9a19cb5b65ea54d982","tid":1563180,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:11:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1dae52cf86fb075379d17cba7d6029bb55a5aa83","tid":1563180,"uid":151578,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"認同搞埋呢個星期可以停停<br />\n<br />\n但的確人鏈有佢作用<br />\n中學生人鏈抗爭成本更低<br />\n亦都可以向街坊宣傳"},{"pid":"8e414d8ca5db1b0365441c43725d665999ca9fd0","tid":1563180,"uid":160847,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得每區搞一兩次就夠<br />\n搞太多其實冇晒意義<br />\n仲會令到其他活動少人左"},{"pid":"0fe6364f4e9266276af5cea056f00cbbecc3f631","tid":1563180,"uid":250586,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"細路搞我覺得無問題，成班成年